data.title: College Announces Fall Honor Roll
data.meta_description: Wake Tech President Dr. Scott Ralls is proud to announce more than 2,000 students made the honor roll for the Fall 2023 semester, up nearly 140 students from the same semester last year.
data.text:
RALEIGH, N.C. (January 4, 2024) â€“ Wake Tech President Dr. Scott Ralls is proud to announce more than 2,000 students made the honor roll for the Fall 2023 semester, up nearly 140 students from the same semester last year.

The 922 students who earned a place on the President's List maintained a grade point average (GPA) of 4.0. The 1,203 students who made the Dean's List maintained a GPA of at least 3.5.

The honor roll recognizes full-time students with a minimum of 12 credit hours in degree programs.
